      "role": "user",
      "content": "yo u ever notice how search autocompletes have been acting super weird lately?? like i was typing stuff about my neighborhood and it kept suggesting phrases that had nothing to do with what i was looking for, almost like it was trying to tell me something or reacting to me specifically. idk if im crazy but it feels intentional",
